OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FDoctors in the Isle of Man are to take
OL,8,Fstrike action for the first time in
OL,9,Fthe island's history.
OL,11,FStaff will will operate under
OL,12,F'Christmas day cover' for two days,
OL,13,Fmeaning emergency care will still be
OL,14,Favailable, but many services will be
OL,15,Flimited.
OL,17,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,18,Fconfirmed the action will take place
OL,19,Fon Wednesday 22 and Thursday 23
OL,20,FJanuary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
