OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FRepresentatives for the BMA say they
OL,8,Fare asking for a 12.6% uplift in pay,
OL,9,Fclaiming doctors have faced a 'real
OL,10,Fterms pay cut since 2008' due to
OL,11,Finflation on the island.
OL,13,FThey say inflation "increased by
OL,14,F56.3%, while the maximum consultant's
OL,15,Fsalary increased by just 27.3% over
OL,16,Fthe same period".
OL,18,FManx Care say while the BMA have given
OL,19,Fthe "minimum notice required" for
OL,20,Faction, they remain in discussions and
OL,21,Fhope to resolve the dispute.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
