OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FIt added that a "further productive
OL,8,Fmeeting was held today with support
OL,9,Ffrom the Manx Industrial Relations
OL,10,FService", and an update will be
OL,11,Fprovided as soon as possible, to
OL,12,Freduce impact and harm to patients and
OL,13,Fservice users.
OL,15,FChair of the Isle of Man Medical
OL,16,FSociety, Dr Prakash Thiagarajan said:
OL,17,F"We have no desire to go on strike,
OL,18,Fbut we made clear to Manx Care that
OL,19,Fthis would be the outcome without an
OL,20,Facceptable pay offer.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
