OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,F"There's still time for an offer to be
OL,8,Fput forward and these strikes averted.
OL,9,FDoctors deserve to be paid fairly for
OL,10,Fthe valuable work they do, and the pay
OL,11,Fcuts we've seen over the last decade
OL,12,Fhave become untenable.
OL,14,F"It's disappointing to find ourselves
OL,15,Fin this position, but the solution is
OL,16,Fclear: restore our lost pay."
OL,18,FDoctors voted overwhelmingly to
OL,19,Fsupport industrial action in December,
OL,20,Fwith 95% siding in favour of the move.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
