OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FProf Phil Banfield, Chair of the BMA
OL,8,Fsaid: "The BMA stands behind Isle of
OL,9,FMan doctors as they make the historic
OL,10,Fdecision to go out on strike for the
OL,11,Fvery first time.
OL,13,F"I've heard from doctors on the Isle
OL,14,Fof Man how badly they wanted to avoid
OL,15,Findustrial action, but they have been
OL,16,Fplaced in an impossible situation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
