OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,F"We trust that Manx Care see how
OL,8,Fserious this issue is, and act quickly
OL,9,Fto provide Isle of Man doctors with a
OL,10,Fcredible pay offer that can avert
OL,11,Fstrike action and values the expertise
OL,12,Fthat doctors bring to the health and
OL,13,Fwell-being of the island."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
