OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the island's
OL,8,FDepartment of Health and Social Care
OL,9,Fadded: "We understand that both Manx
OL,10,FCare and the BMA are currently working
OL,11,Fhard jointly to arrive at a settlement
OL,12,Fthat is both fair on pay and
OL,13,Faffordable within the budget and that
OL,14,Fthe basis of an improved offer is
OL,15,Factively being discussed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
