OL,3,CDoctors in the Isle of Man to strike
OL,4,Cfor first time in history amid pay
OL,5,Cdispute
OL,7,F"In the meantime we respect the right
OL,8,Fof the workforce to take action, and
OL,9,Fwe are working closely with Manx Care
OL,10,Fto support them in reducing the impact
OL,11,Fof any action on patients and the
OL,12,Fpublic.
OL,14,F"In the coming days more information
OL,15,Fwill be made available to patients and
OL,16,Fthe public by Manx Care, once the
OL,17,Fprecise details of the action have
OL,18,Fbecome clearer and mitigation plans
OL,19,Fhave been put in place."
